{"tid":1970721,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"求解夢，琴晚發作個好痴線嘅夢","createTime":"2020-04-13T11:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T11:07:20.000Z","uid":308377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1c6628256df62a5ef360fc4b4ad9309554243c7a","tid":1970721,"uid":308377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:01:09.000Z","msg":"好撚膠下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我一路第一視角<br />\n<br />\n一開頭好正常嘅男人同番個前女友一齊番<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n突然間個女人話比佢聽自己變咗男身女靈魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後個男人佢屋企比個女人同其他人入咗去，成班人做鳩個男人要逼住同個女人一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，然後個男人就話佢好噁心，拒絕咗再跑走。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n落到街男人手機女人嘅朋友及親戚瘋狂炸機，話「條女」好愛佢，個女人就send好多好長嘅文比佢，個男人就關咗手機上網功能。然後手機突然顯示訊息個女人買咗機票，同埋叫個男人同佢去旅行，想做佢老婆。然後個男人話典解我控制唔到自己嘅人生，點解要逼我之類。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為好撚真實，同埋好似feel到個男人嘅情緒起伏，我就嚇醒咗，真係好撚痴線。<br />\n<br />\n有冇高人可以指點下，有咩啟示？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c48178226ea1f9a58bbb897a1b58a7e52908083","tid":1970721,"uid":308377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:07:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}